hivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-T%E1%BA%A5t-t%E1%BB%A9-Di%E1%BB%87u/poem-DNNrtb631qApmvCYm6w9kw">Tặng Tất tứ Diệu - 贈畢四曜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-T%C3%B4-t%E1%BB%A9-H%E1%BB%81/poem-bR8QGem88oZhdNps2IvS6Q">Tặng Tô tứ Hề - 贈蘇四徯</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tra-Th%E1%BA%ADn-H%C3%A0nh/T%E1%BA%A7n-B%C6%B0u-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-trung-t%E1%BB%A9c-m%E1%BB%A5c/poem-62fi-I9SHNrfSNhypwpi_A">Tần Bưu đạo trung tức mục - 秦郵道中即目</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tra-Th%E1%BA%ADn-H%C3%A0nh/author-9xzWBLqDsfopprRgu6Tsgg">Tra Thận Hành</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Thanh-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/T%C3%A2n-gia-ba-tr%C3%BAc-chi-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-9uJ4ouA2HFby6c8TonzRQQ">Tân-gia-ba trúc chi từ kỳ 2 - 新嘉波竹枝詞其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Thanh-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/author-H7U7KCvecgO1KzCd1kGc9A">Phan Thanh Giản</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
